reviewText: The third in the series of The Cisco Kid Collections is another winner. These are the best prints of this series I've ever seen. While they are not crystal clear, they are certainly better than the worn syndicated prints which turn up on local TV stations. Very enjoyable and highly recommended to all vintage TV westerns fans.Volume 4 is rumored to be slated for February, 2005 release. I certainly hope so.
Title: The Cisco Kid - Collection 3

reviewText: Cisco Kid Collection 3 like Collections 1 and 2 are very good I don't know about Collection 4 as I have not seen it yet. I would defintly reocomend it.
Title: The Cisco Kid - Collection 3

reviewText: The picture quality is not perfect, but it's a real treat to see each episode again. Hopefully some company will see the interest in this and other classic TV shows, & digitally remaster them. But again, the picture is not bad at all, and watching these episodes of the Cisco Kid sure beats looking at what Hollywood flings at us today! Each set is worth adding to your collection of good TV westerns.
Title: The Cisco Kid - Collection 3

reviewText: The Cisco Kid - Collection 3Go glad I purchased this video for my Western video collection. Always looking for more.
Title: The Cisco Kid - Collection 3

reviewText: This was an unbeatable deal from Amazon.com. The quality of the product is superb, it arrived in an above average shipping time, and the price was at least $10.00 cheaper than the retail movie store.
Title: The Cisco Kid - Collection 3
